1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,920
Cinco barrios.

2
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:01,760
Una bici.

3
00:00:01,760 --> 00:00:03,480
Y gente increíble
por el camino.

4
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:04,320
Después del trabajo

5
00:00:04,320 --> 00:00:05,560
me pongo
a pedalear.

6
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:07,080
Sin destino,
sin prisa.

7
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:08,120
Solo las calles
y yo.

8
00:00:08,120 --> 00:00:09,920
Es mi manera
de desconectar.

9
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:10,920
Y entre medias,

10
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:12,440
pillo cosas
que la gente deja

11
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:13,480
y aún valen.

12
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:14,040
Las comparto

13
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:15,680
y alguien les
saca partido.

14
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:17,160
Y hay mucha gente
haciendo lo mismo.

15
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,240
En bici,
a pie,

16
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:19,240
como sea.

17
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,640
¿Vosotros tenéis
un plan post-curro

18
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:21,240
así?

19
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:22,040
Contádmelo.

